{"id":2335,"date":"2024-02-28T10:56:41","date_gmt":"2024-02-28T10:56:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.screeningdate.com\/?p=2335"},"modified":"2024-03-30T17:22:52","modified_gmt":"2024-03-30T17:22:52","slug":"how-to-check-mcgill-application-status","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-check-mcgill-application-status\/","title":{"rendered":"How to Check McGill Application Status"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><em><strong>How to Check McGill Application Status, How to accept McGill Admission offer and pay the admission deposit.<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>McGill University Admission is out for all students who applied for admission in the 2024 academic year. Do well to check your application status on https:\/\/<a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"applyjobs.org.ng\">applicant.McGill.ca<\/a>\/to enable you know the required information needed to avoid forfeiting admission.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-check-mcgill-university-application-portal-how-to-check-mcgill-application-status\"><a name=\"_Toc83688578\"><\/a>How to Check McGill University Application Portal| How to Check McGill Application Status<\/h2>\n<p>To view the status of your application, including outstanding necessities, please kindly login in to the McGill online application system to view your admission application status.<\/p>\n<p>Click <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/applicant.McGil.ca\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/applicant.McGil.ca\/<\/a><\/strong> to view McGill University Admission Application Status<\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc83688579\"><\/a><strong>How to accept the offer and pay the Admission Deposit?<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Using your <a href=\"https:\/\/mcgill.ca\/uapply\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>uApply account<\/strong><\/a>, accept your offer of admission and pay the affirmation deposit where relevant.<\/li>\n<li>click <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/mcgill-university-tuition-fees\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/strong> to see fees directives for payment<\/li>\n<li>The next step is to enroll online; an exact date will be issued to you by the university.<\/li>\n<li>Your account will help you track all things you need to know before and after being admitted.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong><em>And now you know how to check your application status by checking your students account we hope this information was helpful kindly drop your comment in the comment box as we look toward your expectations.<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em><strong>Check also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<span class=\"jp-relatedposts-post-title\"><a class=\"jp-relatedposts-post-a\" style=\"color: #800000;\" title=\"Mcgill University Admission 2024 | Application and Deadlines\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/mcgill-university-admission\/?relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=1438&amp;relatedposts_position=2&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=1438&amp;relatedposts_position=2&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=1438&amp;relatedposts_position=2&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=1438&amp;relatedposts_position=2&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=1438&amp;relatedposts_position=2&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=1438&amp;relatedposts_position=2&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=1438&amp;relatedposts_position=2&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=1438&amp;relatedposts_position=2&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=1438&amp;relatedposts_position=2&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=1438&amp;relatedposts_position=2&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=1438&am